item.title: AP source: Retired Gen. Norman Schwarzkopf dies
item.description: MORE: AP source: Retired Gen. Norman Schwarzkopf, who led 1991 Operation Desert Storm, dead at 78: http://t.co/8BnXZsIW -RJJ
item.content:encoded: MORE: AP source: Retired Gen. Norman Schwarzkopf, who led 1991 Operation Desert Storm, dead at 78: http://t.co/8BnXZsIW -RJJ WASHINGTON (AP) — A U.S. official says retired Gen. H. Norman Schwarzkopf, who commanded the U.S.-led international coalition that drove Saddam Hussein's forces out of Kuwait in 1991, has died. He was 78.The official tells The Associated Press that Schwarzkopf died Thursday in Tampa, Fla. The official wasn't authorized to release the information publicly and spoke on condition of anonymity.A much-decorated combat soldier in Vietnam, Schwarzkopf was known popularly as "Stormin' Norman" for a notoriously explosive temper.He lived in retirement in Tampa, where he had served in his last military assignment as commander-in-chief of U.S. Central Command. That is the headquarters responsible for U.S. military and security concerns in nearly 20 countries from the eastern Mediterranean and Africa to Pakistan. Link - Trackbacks

item.description: I uploaded a @YouTube video http://t.co/Q6mINI8g عندما يتكلم حازم الواثق ابو اسماعيل
item.content:encoded: I uploaded a @YouTube video http://t.co/Q6mINI8g عندما يتكلم حازم الواثق ابو اسماعيل http://www.youtube.com/subscription_center?add_user=elbalacona حازم ابو اسماعيل , اسطورة الاحاديث الصحفية و المناظرات و المناورات...الرجل الواثق دائما.. يجعلك تبحر في بحر من الطحينه لترسو على شاطئ من الضحكات على افكاره الفشنك و زعامته الهشه هذا اللينك على صفحتي.. يجاوب على كل الانتقادات التي تتهم الحلقه بالتحيز لجهات بعينها, مصحوب به كل لينكات الفيديوهات الاصلية و مواقع اقتصادية و شرح فني لكل ما اتى بالفيديو و اتحدى ان ياتي احدهم من الفيديوهات الاصلية باي شبهه للقص و اللزق اخرج كلام الاستاذ حازم خارج سياقه.. اكرر اتحدى http://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=450186838371076&set=a.347175812005513.77601.324036264319468&type=1 Link - Trackbacks
